data.description: A rare find - single story, beautiful, Spanish Hacienda with inground swimming pool & spa, walking distance to the popular shops & restaurants of Historic La Mesa Village! With over 2,000 S.F. inside and over 1/3 acre outside, there is plenty of room to spread your wings. Entertain poolside at the outside bar or spacious, 1,200 S.F. covered patio or indoors by the living room or family room fireplaces. Corner lot, Garden of Eden landscaping, arched entries, large kitchen, carport and garage. A++ location!
